      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready for a dependable daily driver with plenty of character! This car is in fair condition and has been a reliable companion on the road. While it shows some honest wear and tear from its years of service, it still runs well and offers a solid, functional driving experience for anyone looking for great value!",
