    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its ownership. The engine runs smoothly and the transmission shifts as it should, making it a dependable choice for any driver. While the exterior is generally clean, you may find minor stone chips and light surface scratches consistent with regular use. Inside, the cabin is tidy with minimal wear on the upholstery, and all major electronics are fully functional. It\u2019s a solid, reliable car that is ready for its next owner.",
