    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and a few small dings, and the interior upholstery shows significant wear and some staining in the footwells. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, but it will eventually need attention for a slow power steering leak and a suspension that has become somewhat stiff over time. It\u2019s a solid choice for someone looking for a functional vehicle who doesn't mind a bit of cosmetic patina and some upcoming minor maintenance tasks.",
      "price": 20000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
